<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Adobe Systems.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Adobe Systems.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Hambrecht &amp; Quist said it raised fiscal 1997 earnings estimates for Adobe Systems Inc to $2.35 a share from $2.25 a share and fiscal 1998 to $2.70 a share from $2.65.</p>
<p>-- Late Tuesday, Adobe posted a profit of $45.4 million, or $0.61 a share, before a gain in its fiscal first quarter ended February 28, versus $32 million, or $0.42 a share one year ago.</p>
<p>-- In a statement, Hambrecht &amp; Quist noted the company's earnings report showed improved gross margins and tight expense controls. Also its PhotoShop 4 and PageMaker software continue to show strong sales.</p>
